      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Turnbull lake case is still\noccupying the attention of Judge\nBelts court.\n\n\nJudge KEENAN, is handling some\nprobate matters this morning and\nit is possible that the usual matt\nnee which is due in the divorce\nmill will be postponed ON account\nOF the prosecuting attorney being\nidentified with the Anderson murder\ntrial. There are three applicants\nfor divorce, however, waiting the\npleasure of the Judge."
